<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

{{ include('shared/header.twig') }}

<body>
    {{ include('shared/nav.twig') }}

  <!-- Services section-->
  <section class="bg-light py-5 border-bottom">
    <div class="container px-5 my-5">
      <div class="text-center mb-5">
        <h2 class="fw-bolder">Tutoring Services</h2>
        <p class="lead mb-0">Information and Frequently Asked Questions</p>
      </div>
      <div class="row gx-5 justify-content-center">
        <div class="accordion" id="accordionExample">
          <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingOne">
              <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                data-bs-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                In-Person Tutoring
              </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingOne"
              data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
              <div class="accordion-body">
                <strong>In-person tutoring takes place in Sarasota.</strong> Your tutor meets you at the Fruitville
                Public Library at the intersection of Fruitville Rd and Lake Wood Ranch Blvd.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingTwo">
              <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                Online Tutoring
              </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo"
              data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
              <div class="accordion-body">
                <strong>Online tutoring takes place via zoom.</strong> Your tutor will send you a zoom meeting
                invitation at least 24 hours before your scheduled meeting time.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingThree">
              <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                Group Tutoring Sessions
              </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree"
              data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
              <div class="accordion-body">
                <strong>Meet in groups with up to four students.</strong> Invite your classmates to make your own group,
                or join one of the other tutoring groups that are at the same level as you.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingFour">
              <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                data-bs-target="#collapseFour" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFour">
                Prepare For Your Tutoring Session
              </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="collapseFour" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFour"
              data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
              <div class="accordion-body">
                <strong>Send your tutor information on what you want to work on before your tutoring session.</strong>
                Sessions can go a bit smoother if you provide your tutor with some information before you start. While
                this in not required, it allows your tutor to come to the session better prepared to give you the best
                tutoring services possible.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingFive">
              <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                data-bs-target="#collapseFive" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFive">
                Session Recommendations
              </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="collapseFive" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFive"
              data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
              <div class="accordion-body">
                <strong>We recommend that you meet with your tutor 2 times per week.</strong> While our tutoring
                services are flexible to work with your schedule, many students see the best results when they do 2
                sessions per week, 1.5 hours per session.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

    {{ include('shared/footer.twig') }}
    {{ include('shared/script.twig') }}
</body>

</html>